name: Bench on Demand
overview:
Proven offshore development on your terms

The team at Bench On Demand has been using an offshore software development model for close to seven years. We have several methodologies and processes in place such as a comprehensive Project Management platform to ensure your project is successful. The team at Bench On Demand offers on-demand, just-in-time software development. You define when how many programmers to assign, when the project starts, when it ends, and what the programmers work on.

Teams you can Demand Application Development and Maintenance Open source consulting and implementation Linux / Apache / PHP / Mysql Microsoft Solutions SOA / Web Services Support / Help Desk services Internet Marketing QA / Testing Services
